text: Excellent service. The shop has literally any item you need and they are very price friendly. Delivery is free too which is amazing. Their vegetables are fresh and of good quality. So glad to find this store and definitely making it my go to store. Highly recommend!!

I visited Singa groceries last week and found the shop to be very organised and clean. Also, the highlight is that they sell things comparatively at low price when compared to other mini marts and shops and one can witness that when they shop there..Also,  there's no compromise in the quality of the products...Veggies were super fresh...it's almost like a onestop shop and 5 stars to their customer service....Highly recommend!!!!!
